    SELECT TOP(1) [s].[StatusId]
    FROM [Job].[AppliedJobs] AS [s]
    WHERE (([s].[CandidateId] = [m].[CandidateId]) AND ([s].[JobId] = [m].[JobId])) AND ([s].[CompanyId] = [m].[CompanyId])
    ORDER BY [s].[ApplicationId] DESC
), 0) AS [StatusId], [a].[ApplicationId], CAST(COALESCE((
    SELECT TOP(1) [sm].[IsReceivedCandidate]
    FROM [Common].[Message] AS [sm]
    WHERE (([sm].[CandidateId] = [m].[CandidateId]) AND ([sm].[JobId] = [m].[JobId])) AND ([sm].[CompanyId] = [m].[CompanyId])
    ORDER BY [sm].[SendingTime] DESC
), 0) AS bit) AS [IsReceivedCandidate], CAST(COALESCE((
    SELECT TOP(1) [sm0].[IsReceivedEmploye]
    FROM [Common].[Message] AS [sm0]
    WHERE (([sm0].[CandidateId] = [m].[CandidateId]) AND ([sm0].[JobId] = [m].[JobId])) AND ([sm0].[CompanyId] = [m].[CompanyId])
    ORDER BY [sm0].[SendingTime] DESC
), 0) AS bit) AS [IsReceivedEmploye], COALESCE((
    SELECT TOP(1) [sm1].[SendingTime]
    FROM [Common].[Message] AS [sm1]
    WHERE (([sm1].[CandidateId] = [m].[CandidateId]) AND ([sm1].[JobId] = [m].[JobId])) AND ([sm1].[CompanyId] = [m].[CompanyId])
    ORDER BY [sm1].[SendingTime] DESC
), '0001-01-01T00:00:00.000') AS [LastSendingTime], (
    SELECT TOP(1) [sm2].[MessageBody]
    FROM [Common].[Message] AS [sm2]
    WHERE ((([sm2].[CandidateId] = [m].[CandidateId]) AND ([sm2].[JobId] = [m].[JobId])) AND ([sm2].[CompanyId] = [m].[CompanyId])) AND ([sm2].[IsDelete] = 0)
    ORDER BY [sm2].[SendingTime] DESC
) AS [LastSendingMessage]
FROM [Common].[Message] AS [m]
INNER JOIN [Job].[Companies] AS [c] ON [m].[CompanyId] = [c].[CompanyId]
INNER JOIN [Job].[Jobs] AS [j] ON [m].[JobId] = [j].[JobId]
INNER JOIN [Job].[AppliedJobs] AS [a] ON [m].[CompanyId] = [a].[CompanyId]

    WHERE (([s].[CandidateId] = [m].[CandidateId]) AND ([s].[JobId] = [m].[JobId])) AND ([s].[CompanyId] = [m].[CompanyId])
    ORDER BY [s].[ApplicationId] DESC
), 0) AS [StatusId], [a].[ApplicationId], CAST(COALESCE((
    SELECT TOP(1) [sm].[IsReceivedCandidate]
    FROM [Common].[Message] AS [sm]
    WHERE (([sm].[CandidateId] = [m].[CandidateId]) AND ([sm].[JobId] = [m].[JobId])) AND ([sm].[CompanyId] = [m].[CompanyId])

SELECT DISTINCT [m].[CandidateId], [m].[JobId], [j].[JobTitle], [m].[CompanyId], [c].[CompanyName], COALESCE((
    SELECT TOP(1) [s].[StatusId]
    FROM [Job].[AppliedJobs] AS [s]
    WHERE (([s].[CandidateId] = [m].[CandidateId]) AND ([s].[JobId] = [m].[JobId])) AND ([s].[CompanyId] = [m].[CompanyId])
    ORDER BY [s].[ApplicationId] DESC
), 0) AS [StatusId], [a].[ApplicationId], CAST(COALESCE((
    SELECT TOP(1) [sm].[IsReceivedCandidate]
    FROM [Common].[Message] AS [sm]
    WHERE (([sm].[CandidateId] = [m].[CandidateId]) AND ([sm].[JobId] = [m].[JobId])) AND ([sm].[CompanyId] = [m].[CompanyId])
    ORDER BY [sm].[SendingTime] DESC
), 0) AS bit) AS [IsReceivedCandidate], CAST(COALESCE((
    SELECT TOP(1) [sm0].[IsReceivedEmploye]
    FROM [Common].[Message] AS [sm0]
    WHERE (([sm0].[CandidateId] = [m].[CandidateId]) AND ([sm0].[JobId] = [m].[JobId])) AND ([sm0].[CompanyId] = [m].[CompanyId])
    ORDER BY [sm0].[SendingTime] DESC
), 0) AS bit) AS [IsReceivedEmploye], COALESCE((
    SELECT TOP(1) [sm1].[SendingTime]
    FROM [Common].[Message] AS [sm1]
    WHERE (([sm1].[CandidateId] = [m].[CandidateId]) AND ([sm1].[JobId] = [m].[JobId])) AND ([sm1].[CompanyId] = [m].[CompanyId])
    ORDER BY [sm1].[SendingTime] DESC
), '0001-01-01T00:00:00.000') AS [LastSendingTime], (
    SELECT TOP(1) [sm2].[MessageBody]
    FROM [Common].[Message] AS [sm2]
    WHERE ((([sm2].[CandidateId] = [m].[CandidateId]) AND ([sm2].[JobId] = [m].[JobId])) AND ([sm2].[CompanyId] = [m].[CompanyId])) AND ([sm2].[IsDelete] = 0)
    ORDER BY [sm2].[SendingTime] DESC
) AS [LastSendingMessage]
FROM [Common].[Message] AS [m]
INNER JOIN [Job].[Companies] AS [c] ON [m].[CompanyId] = [c].[CompanyId]
INNER JOIN [Job].[Jobs] AS [j] ON [m].[JobId] = [j].[JobId]
INNER JOIN [Job].[AppliedJobs] AS [a] ON [m].[CompanyId] = [a].[CompanyId]
WHERE ((([a].[JobId] = [m].[JobId]) AND ([m].[CandidateId] = @__candidateId_0)) AND ([m].[IsDelete] = 0)) AND ([a].[CandidateId] = @__candidateId_0)

SELECT DISTINCT [m].[CandidateId], [m].[JobId], [j].[JobTitle], [m].[CompanyId], [c].[CompanyName], COALESCE((
    SELECT TOP(1) [s].[StatusId]
    FROM [Job].[AppliedJobs] AS [s]
    WHERE (([s].[CandidateId] = [m].[CandidateId]) AND ([s].[JobId] = [m].[JobId])) AND ([s].[CompanyId] = [m].[CompanyId])
    ORDER BY [s].[ApplicationId] DESC
), 0) AS [StatusId], [a].[ApplicationId], CAST(COALESCE((
    SELECT TOP(1) [sm].[IsReceivedCandidate]
    FROM [Common].[Message] AS [sm]
    WHERE (([sm].[CandidateId] = [m].[CandidateId]) AND ([sm].[JobId] = [m].[JobId])) AND ([sm].[CompanyId] = [m].[CompanyId])
    ORDER BY [sm].[SendingTime] DESC
), 0) AS bit) AS [IsReceivedCandidate], CAST(COALESCE((
    SELECT TOP(1) [sm0].[IsReceivedEmploye]
    FROM [Common].[Message] AS [sm0]
    WHERE (([sm0].[CandidateId] = [m].[CandidateId]) AND ([sm0].[JobId] = [m].[JobId])) AND ([sm0].[CompanyId] = [m].[CompanyId])
    ORDER BY [sm0].[SendingTime] DESC
), 0) AS bit) AS [IsReceivedEmploye], COALESCE((
    SELECT TOP(1) [sm1].[SendingTime]
    FROM [Common].[Message] AS [sm1]
    WHERE (([sm1].[CandidateId] = [m].[CandidateId]) AND ([sm1].[JobId] = [m].[JobId])) AND ([sm1].[CompanyId] = [m].[CompanyId])
    ORDER BY [sm1].[SendingTime] DESC
), '0001-01-01T00:00:00.000') AS [LastSendingTime], (
    SELECT TOP(1) [sm2].[MessageBody]
    FROM [Common].[Message] AS [sm2]
    WHERE ((([sm2].[CandidateId] = [m].[CandidateId]) AND ([sm2].[JobId] = [m].[JobId])) AND ([sm2].[CompanyId] = [m].[CompanyId])) AND ([sm2].[IsDelete] = 0)
    ORDER BY [sm2].[SendingTime] DESC
) AS [LastSendingMessage]
FROM [Common].[Message] AS [m]
INNER JOIN [Job].[Companies] AS [c] ON [m].[CompanyId] = [c].[CompanyId]
INNER JOIN [Job].[Jobs] AS [j] ON [m].[JobId] = [j].[JobId]
INNER JOIN [Job].[AppliedJobs] AS [a] ON [m].[CompanyId] = [a].[CompanyId]
WHERE ((([a].[JobId] = [m].[JobId]) AND ([m].[CandidateId] = @__candidateId_0)) AND ([m].[IsDelete] = 0)) AND ([a].[CandidateId] = @__candidateId_0)

SELECT DISTINCT [m].[CandidateId], [m].[JobId], [j].[JobTitle], [m].[CompanyId], [c].[CompanyName], COALESCE((
    SELECT TOP(1) [s].[StatusId]
    FROM [Job].[AppliedJobs] AS [s]
    WHERE (([s].[CandidateId] = [m].[CandidateId]) AND ([s].[JobId] = [m].[JobId])) AND ([s].[CompanyId] = [m].[CompanyId])
    ORDER BY [s].[ApplicationId] DESC
), 0) AS [StatusId], [a].[ApplicationId], CAST(COALESCE((
    SELECT TOP(1) [sm].[IsReceivedCandidate]
    FROM [Common].[Message] AS [sm]
    WHERE (([sm].[CandidateId] = [m].[CandidateId]) AND ([sm].[JobId] = [m].[JobId])) AND ([sm].[CompanyId] = [m].[CompanyId])
    ORDER BY [sm].[SendingTime] DESC
), 0) AS bit) AS [IsReceivedCandidate], CAST(COALESCE((
    SELECT TOP(1) [sm0].[IsReceivedEmploye]
    FROM [Common].[Message] AS [sm0]
    WHERE (([sm0].[CandidateId] = [m].[CandidateId]) AND ([sm0].[JobId] = [m].[JobId])) AND ([sm0].[CompanyId] = [m].[CompanyId])
    ORDER BY [sm0].[SendingTime] DESC
), 0) AS bit) AS [IsReceivedEmploye], COALESCE((
    SELECT TOP(1) [sm1].[SendingTime]
    FROM [Common].[Message] AS [sm1]
    WHERE (([sm1].[CandidateId] = [m].[CandidateId]) AND ([sm1].[JobId] = [m].[JobId])) AND ([sm1].[CompanyId] = [m].[CompanyId])
    ORDER BY [sm1].[SendingTime] DESC
), '0001-01-01T00:00:00.000') AS [LastSendingTime], (
    SELECT TOP(1) [sm2].[MessageBody]
    FROM [Common].[Message] AS [sm2]
    WHERE ((([sm2].[CandidateId] = [m].[CandidateId]) AND ([sm2].[JobId] = [m].[JobId])) AND ([sm2].[CompanyId] = [m].[CompanyId])) AND ([sm2].[IsDelete] = 0)
    ORDER BY [sm2].[SendingTime] DESC
) AS [LastSendingMessage]
FROM [Common].[Message] AS [m]
INNER JOIN [Job].[Companies] AS [c] ON [m].[CompanyId] = [c].[CompanyId]
INNER JOIN [Job].[Jobs] AS [j] ON [m].[JobId] = [j].[JobId]
INNER JOIN [Job].[AppliedJobs] AS [a] ON [m].[CompanyId] = [a].[CompanyId]
WHERE ((([a].[JobId] = [m].[JobId]) AND ([m].[CandidateId] = @__candidateId_0)) AND ([m].[IsDelete] = 0)) AND ([a].[CandidateId] = @__candidateId_0)

SELECT DISTINCT [m].[CandidateId], [m].[JobId], [j].[JobTitle], [m].[CompanyId], [c].[CompanyName], COALESCE((
    SELECT TOP(1) [s].[StatusId]
    FROM [Job].[AppliedJobs] AS [s]
    WHERE (([s].[CandidateId] = [m].[CandidateId]) AND ([s].[JobId] = [m].[JobId])) AND ([s].[CompanyId] = [m].[CompanyId])
    ORDER BY [s].[ApplicationId] DESC
), 0) AS [StatusId], [a].[ApplicationId], CAST(COALESCE((
    SELECT TOP(1) [sm].[IsReceivedCandidate]
    FROM [Common].[Message] AS [sm]
    WHERE (([sm].[CandidateId] = [m].[CandidateId]) AND ([sm].[JobId] = [m].[JobId])) AND ([sm].[CompanyId] = [m].[CompanyId])
    ORDER BY [sm].[SendingTime] DESC
), 0) AS bit) AS [IsReceivedCandidate], CAST(COALESCE((
    SELECT TOP(1) [sm0].[IsReceivedEmploye]
    FROM [Common].[Message] AS [sm0]
    WHERE (([sm0].[CandidateId] = [m].[CandidateId]) AND ([sm0].[JobId] = [m].[JobId])) AND ([sm0].[CompanyId] = [m].[CompanyId])
    ORDER BY [sm0].[SendingTime] DESC
), 0) AS bit) AS [IsReceivedEmploye], COALESCE((
    SELECT TOP(1) [sm1].[SendingTime]
    FROM [Common].[Message] AS [sm1]
    WHERE (([sm1].[CandidateId] = [m].[CandidateId]) AND ([sm1].[JobId] = [m].[JobId])) AND ([sm1].[CompanyId] = [m].[CompanyId])
    ORDER BY [sm1].[SendingTime] DESC
), '0001-01-01T00:00:00.000') AS [LastSendingTime], (
    SELECT TOP(1) [sm2].[MessageBody]
    FROM [Common].[Message] AS [sm2]
    WHERE ((([sm2].[CandidateId] = [m].[CandidateId]) AND ([sm2].[JobId] = [m].[JobId])) AND ([sm2].[CompanyId] = [m].[CompanyId])) AND ([sm2].[IsDelete] = 0)
    ORDER BY [sm2].[SendingTime] DESC
) AS [LastSendingMessage]
FROM [Common].[Message] AS [m]
INNER JOIN [Job].[Companies] AS [c] ON [m].[CompanyId] = [c].[CompanyId]
INNER JOIN [Job].[Jobs] AS [j] ON [m].[JobId] = [j].[JobId]
INNER JOIN [Job].[AppliedJobs] AS [a] ON [m].[CompanyId] = [a].[CompanyId]
WHERE ((([a].[JobId] = [m].[JobId]) AND ([m].[CandidateId] = @__candidateId_0)) AND ([m].[IsDelete] = 0)) AND ([a].[CandidateId] = @__candidateId_0)

SELECT DISTINCT [m].[CandidateId], [m].[JobId], [j].[JobTitle], [m].[CompanyId], [c].[CompanyName], COALESCE((
    SELECT TOP(1) [s].[StatusId]
    FROM [Job].[AppliedJobs] AS [s]
    WHERE (([s].[CandidateId] = [m].[CandidateId]) AND ([s].[JobId] = [m].[JobId])) AND ([s].[CompanyId] = [m].[CompanyId])
    ORDER BY [s].[ApplicationId] DESC
), 0) AS [StatusId], [a].[ApplicationId], CAST(COALESCE((
    SELECT TOP(1) [sm].[IsReceivedCandidate]
    FROM [Common].[Message] AS [sm]
    WHERE (([sm].[CandidateId] = [m].[CandidateId]) AND ([sm].[JobId] = [m].[JobId])) AND ([sm].[CompanyId] = [m].[CompanyId])
    ORDER BY [sm].[SendingTime] DESC
), 0) AS bit) AS [IsReceivedCandidate], CAST(COALESCE((
    SELECT TOP(1) [sm0].[IsReceivedEmploye]
    FROM [Common].[Message] AS [sm0]
    WHERE (([sm0].[CandidateId] = [m].[CandidateId]) AND ([sm0].[JobId] = [m].[JobId])) AND ([sm0].[CompanyId] = [m].[CompanyId])
    ORDER BY [sm0].[SendingTime] DESC
), 0) AS bit) AS [IsReceivedEmploye], COALESCE((
    SELECT TOP(1) [sm1].[SendingTime]
    FROM [Common].[Message] AS [sm1]
    WHERE (([sm1].[CandidateId] = [m].[CandidateId]) AND ([sm1].[JobId] = [m].[JobId])) AND ([sm1].[CompanyId] = [m].[CompanyId])
    ORDER BY [sm1].[SendingTime] DESC
), '0001-01-01T00:00:00.000') AS [LastSendingTime], (
    SELECT TOP(1) [sm2].[MessageBody]
    FROM [Common].[Message] AS [sm2]
    WHERE ((([sm2].[CandidateId] = [m].[CandidateId]) AND ([sm2].[JobId] = [m].[JobId])) AND ([sm2].[CompanyId] = [m].[CompanyId])) AND ([sm2].[IsDelete] = 0)
    ORDER BY [sm2].[SendingTime] DESC
) AS [LastSendingMessage]
FROM [Common].[Message] AS [m]
INNER JOIN [Job].[Companies] AS [c] ON [m].[CompanyId] = [c].[CompanyId]
INNER JOIN [Job].[Jobs] AS [j] ON [m].[JobId] = [j].[JobId]
INNER JOIN [Job].[AppliedJobs] AS [a] ON [m].[CompanyId] = [a].[CompanyId]
WHERE ((([a].[JobId] = [m].[JobId]) AND ([m].[CandidateId] = @__candidateId_0)) AND ([m].[IsDelete] = 0)) AND ([a].[CandidateId] = @__candidateId_0)

SELECT DISTINCT [m].[CandidateId], [m].[JobId], [j].[JobTitle], [m].[CompanyId], [c].[CompanyName], COALESCE((
    SELECT TOP(1) [s].[StatusId]
    FROM [Job].[AppliedJobs] AS [s]
    WHERE (([s].[CandidateId] = [m].[CandidateId]) AND ([s].[JobId] = [m].[JobId])) AND ([s].[CompanyId] = [m].[CompanyId])
    ORDER BY [s].[ApplicationId] DESC
), 0) AS [StatusId], [a].[ApplicationId], CAST(COALESCE((
    SELECT TOP(1) [sm].[IsReceivedCandidate]
    FROM [Common].[Message] AS [sm]
    WHERE (([sm].[CandidateId] = [m].[CandidateId]) AND ([sm].[JobId] = [m].[JobId])) AND ([sm].[CompanyId] = [m].[CompanyId])
    ORDER BY [sm].[SendingTime] DESC
), 0) AS bit) AS [IsReceivedCandidate], CAST(COALESCE((
    SELECT TOP(1) [sm0].[IsReceivedEmploye]
    FROM [Common].[Message] AS [sm0]
    WHERE (([sm0].[CandidateId] = [m].[CandidateId]) AND ([sm0].[JobId] = [m].[JobId])) AND ([sm0].[CompanyId] = [m].[CompanyId])
    ORDER BY [sm0].[SendingTime] DESC
), 0) AS bit) AS [IsReceivedEmploye], COALESCE((
    SELECT TOP(1) [sm1].[SendingTime]
    FROM [Common].[Message] AS [sm1]
    WHERE (([sm1].[CandidateId] = [m].[CandidateId]) AND ([sm1].[JobId] = [m].[JobId])) AND ([sm1].[CompanyId] = [m].[CompanyId])
    ORDER BY [sm1].[SendingTime] DESC
), '0001-01-01T00:00:00.000') AS [LastSendingTime], (
    SELECT TOP(1) [sm2].[MessageBody]
    FROM [Common].[Message] AS [sm2]
    WHERE ((([sm2].[CandidateId] = [m].[CandidateId]) AND ([sm2].[JobId] = [m].[JobId])) AND ([sm2].[CompanyId] = [m].[CompanyId])) AND ([sm2].[IsDelete] = 0)
    ORDER BY [sm2].[SendingTime] DESC
) AS [LastSendingMessage]
FROM [Common].[Message] AS [m]
INNER JOIN [Job].[Companies] AS [c] ON [m].[CompanyId] = [c].[CompanyId]
INNER JOIN [Job].[Jobs] AS [j] ON [m].[JobId] = [j].[JobId]
INNER JOIN [Job].[AppliedJobs] AS [a] ON [m].[CompanyId] = [a].[CompanyId]
WHERE ((([a].[JobId] = [m].[JobId]) AND ([m].[CandidateId] = @__candidateId_0)) AND ([m].[IsDelete] = 0)) AND ([a].[CandidateId] = @__candidateId_0)

SELECT DISTINCT [m].[CandidateId], [m].[JobId], [j].[JobTitle], [m].[CompanyId], [c].[CompanyName], COALESCE((
    SELECT TOP(1) [s].[StatusId]
    FROM [Job].[AppliedJobs] AS [s]
    WHERE (([s].[CandidateId] = [m].[CandidateId]) AND ([s].[JobId] = [m].[JobId])) AND ([s].[CompanyId] = [m].[CompanyId])
    ORDER BY [s].[ApplicationId] DESC
), 0) AS [StatusId], [a].[ApplicationId], CAST(COALESCE((
    SELECT TOP(1) [sm].[IsReceivedCandidate]
    FROM [Common].[Message] AS [sm]
    WHERE (([sm].[CandidateId] = [m].[CandidateId]) AND ([sm].[JobId] = [m].[JobId])) AND ([sm].[CompanyId] = [m].[CompanyId])
    ORDER BY [sm].[SendingTime] DESC
), 0) AS bit) AS [IsReceivedCandidate], CAST(COALESCE((
    SELECT TOP(1) [sm0].[IsReceivedEmploye]
    FROM [Common].[Message] AS [sm0]
    WHERE (([sm0].[CandidateId] = [m].[CandidateId]) AND ([sm0].[JobId] = [m].[JobId])) AND ([sm0].[CompanyId] = [m].[CompanyId])
    ORDER BY [sm0].[SendingTime] DESC
), 0) AS bit) AS [IsReceivedEmploye], COALESCE((
    SELECT TOP(1) [sm1].[SendingTime]
    FROM [Common].[Message] AS [sm1]
    WHERE (([sm1].[CandidateId] = [m].[CandidateId]) AND ([sm1].[JobId] = [m].[JobId])) AND ([sm1].[CompanyId] = [m].[CompanyId])
    ORDER BY [sm1].[SendingTime] DESC
), '0001-01-01T00:00:00.000') AS [LastSendingTime], (
    SELECT TOP(1) [sm2].[MessageBody]
    FROM [Common].[Message] AS [sm2]
    WHERE ((([sm2].[CandidateId] = [m].[CandidateId]) AND ([sm2].[JobId] = [m].[JobId])) AND ([sm2].[CompanyId] = [m].[CompanyId])) AND ([sm2].[IsDelete] = 0)
    ORDER BY [sm2].[SendingTime] DESC
) AS [LastSendingMessage]
FROM [Common].[Message] AS [m]
INNER JOIN [Job].[Companies] AS [c] ON [m].[CompanyId] = [c].[CompanyId]
INNER JOIN [Job].[Jobs] AS [j] ON [m].[JobId] = [j].[JobId]
INNER JOIN [Job].[AppliedJobs] AS [a] ON [m].[CompanyId] = [a].[CompanyId]
WHERE ((([a].[JobId] = [m].[JobId]) AND ([m].[CandidateId] = @__candidateId_0)) AND ([m].[IsDelete] = 0)) AND ([a].[CandidateId] = @__candidateId_0)

SELECT DISTINCT [m].[CandidateId], [m].[JobId], [j].[JobTitle], [m].[CompanyId], [c].[CompanyName], COALESCE((
    SELECT TOP(1) [s].[StatusId]
    FROM [Job].[AppliedJobs] AS [s]
    WHERE (([s].[CandidateId] = [m].[CandidateId]) AND ([s].[JobId] = [m].[JobId])) AND ([s].[CompanyId] = [m].[CompanyId])
    ORDER BY [s].[ApplicationId] DESC
), 0) AS [StatusId], [a].[ApplicationId], CAST(COALESCE((
    SELECT TOP(1) [sm].[IsReceivedCandidate]
    FROM [Common].[Message] AS [sm]
    WHERE (([sm].[CandidateId] = [m].[CandidateId]) AND ([sm].[JobId] = [m].[JobId])) AND ([sm].[CompanyId] = [m].[CompanyId])
    ORDER BY [sm].[SendingTime] DESC
), 0) AS bit) AS [IsReceivedCandidate], CAST(COALESCE((
    SELECT TOP(1) [sm0].[IsReceivedEmploye]
    FROM [Common].[Message] AS [sm0]
    WHERE (([sm0].[CandidateId] = [m].[CandidateId]) AND ([sm0].[JobId] = [m].[JobId])) AND ([sm0].[CompanyId] = [m].[CompanyId])
    ORDER BY [sm0].[SendingTime] DESC
), 0) AS bit) AS [IsReceivedEmploye], COALESCE((
    SELECT TOP(1) [sm1].[SendingTime]
    FROM [Common].[Message] AS [sm1]
    WHERE (([sm1].[CandidateId] = [m].[CandidateId]) AND ([sm1].[JobId] = [m].[JobId])) AND ([sm1].[CompanyId] = [m].[CompanyId])
    ORDER BY [sm1].[SendingTime] DESC
), '0001-01-01T00:00:00.000') AS [LastSendingTime], (
    SELECT TOP(1) [sm2].[MessageBody]
    FROM [Common].[Message] AS [sm2]
    WHERE ((([sm2].[CandidateId] = [m].[CandidateId]) AND ([sm2].[JobId] = [m].[JobId])) AND ([sm2].[CompanyId] = [m].[CompanyId])) AND ([sm2].[IsDelete] = 0)
    ORDER BY [sm2].[SendingTime] DESC
) AS [LastSendingMessage]
FROM [Common].[Message] AS [m]
INNER JOIN [Job].[Companies] AS [c] ON [m].[CompanyId] = [c].[CompanyId]
INNER JOIN [Job].[Jobs] AS [j] ON [m].[JobId] = [j].[JobId]
INNER JOIN [Job].[AppliedJobs] AS [a] ON [m].[CompanyId] = [a].[CompanyId]
WHERE ((([a].[JobId] = [m].[JobId]) AND ([m].[CandidateId] = @__candidateId_0)) AND ([m].[IsDelete] = 0)) AND ([a].[CandidateId] = @__candidateId_0)

SELECT DISTINCT [m].[CandidateId], [m].[JobId], [j].[JobTitle], [m].[CompanyId], [c].[CompanyName], COALESCE((
    SELECT TOP(1) [s].[StatusId]
    FROM [Job].[AppliedJobs] AS [s]
    WHERE (([s].[CandidateId] = [m].[CandidateId]) AND ([s].[JobId] = [m].[JobId])) AND ([s].[CompanyId] = [m].[CompanyId])
    ORDER BY [s].[ApplicationId] DESC
), 0) AS [StatusId], [a].[ApplicationId], CAST(COALESCE((
    SELECT TOP(1) [sm].[IsReceivedCandidate]
    FROM [Common].[Message] AS [sm]
    WHERE (([sm].[CandidateId] = [m].[CandidateId]) AND ([sm].[JobId] = [m].[JobId])) AND ([sm].[CompanyId] = [m].[CompanyId])
    ORDER BY [sm].[SendingTime] DESC
), 0) AS bit) AS [IsReceivedCandidate], CAST(COALESCE((
    SELECT TOP(1) [sm0].[IsReceivedEmploye]
    FROM [Common].[Message] AS [sm0]
    WHERE (([sm0].[CandidateId] = [m].[CandidateId]) AND ([sm0].[JobId] = [m].[JobId])) AND ([sm0].[CompanyId] = [m].[CompanyId])
    ORDER BY [sm0].[SendingTime] DESC
), 0) AS bit) AS [IsReceivedEmploye], COALESCE((
    SELECT TOP(1) [sm1].[SendingTime]
    FROM [Common].[Message] AS [sm1]
    WHERE (([sm1].[CandidateId] = [m].[CandidateId]) AND ([sm1].[JobId] = [m].[JobId])) AND ([sm1].[CompanyId] = [m].[CompanyId])
    ORDER BY [sm1].[SendingTime] DESC
), '0001-01-01T00:00:00.000') AS [LastSendingTime], (
    SELECT TOP(1) [sm2].[MessageBody]
    FROM [Common].[Message] AS [sm2]
    WHERE ((([sm2].[CandidateId] = [m].[CandidateId]) AND ([sm2].[JobId] = [m].[JobId])) AND ([sm2].[CompanyId] = [m].[CompanyId])) AND ([sm2].[IsDelete] = 0)
    ORDER BY [sm2].[SendingTime] DESC
) AS [LastSendingMessage]
FROM [Common].[Message] AS [m]
INNER JOIN [Job].[Companies] AS [c] ON [m].[CompanyId] = [c].[CompanyId]
INNER JOIN [Job].[Jobs] AS [j] ON [m].[JobId] = [j].[JobId]
INNER JOIN [Job].[AppliedJobs] AS [a] ON [m].[CompanyId] = [a].[CompanyId]
WHERE ((([a].[JobId] = [m].[JobId]) AND ([m].[CandidateId] = @__candidateId_0)) AND ([m].[IsDelete] = 0)) AND ([a].[CandidateId] = @__candidateId_0)

SELECT DISTINCT [m].[CandidateId], [m].[JobId], [j].[JobTitle], [m].[CompanyId], [c].[CompanyName], COALESCE((
    SELECT TOP(1) [s].[StatusId]
    FROM [Job].[AppliedJobs] AS [s]
    WHERE (([s].[CandidateId] = [m].[CandidateId]) AND ([s].[JobId] = [m].[JobId])) AND ([s].[CompanyId] = [m].[CompanyId])
    ORDER BY [s].[ApplicationId] DESC
), 0) AS [StatusId], [a].[ApplicationId], CAST(COALESCE((
    SELECT TOP(1) [sm].[IsReceivedCandidate]
    FROM [Common].[Message] AS [sm]
    WHERE (([sm].[CandidateId] = [m].[CandidateId]) AND ([sm].[JobId] = [m].[JobId])) AND ([sm].[CompanyId] = [m].[CompanyId])
    ORDER BY [sm].[SendingTime] DESC
), 0) AS bit) AS [IsReceivedCandidate], CAST(COALESCE((
    SELECT TOP(1) [sm0].[IsReceivedEmploye]
    FROM [Common].[Message] AS [sm0]
    WHERE (([sm0].[CandidateId] = [m].[CandidateId]) AND ([sm0].[JobId] = [m].[JobId])) AND ([sm0].[CompanyId] = [m].[CompanyId])
    ORDER BY [sm0].[SendingTime] DESC
), 0) AS bit) AS [IsReceivedEmploye], COALESCE((
    SELECT TOP(1) [sm1].[SendingTime]
    FROM [Common].[Message] AS [sm1]
    WHERE (([sm1].[CandidateId] = [m].[CandidateId]) AND ([sm1].[JobId] = [m].[JobId])) AND ([sm1].[CompanyId] = [m].[CompanyId])
    ORDER BY [sm1].[SendingTime] DESC
), '0001-01-01T00:00:00.000') AS [LastSendingTime], (
    SELECT TOP(1) [sm2].[MessageBody]
    FROM [Common].[Message] AS [sm2]
    WHERE ((([sm2].[CandidateId] = [m].[CandidateId]) AND ([sm2].[JobId] = [m].[JobId])) AND ([sm2].[CompanyId] = [m].[CompanyId])) AND ([sm2].[IsDelete] = 0)
    ORDER BY [sm2].[SendingTime] DESC
) AS [LastSendingMessage]
FROM [Common].[Message] AS [m]
INNER JOIN [Job].[Companies] AS [c] ON [m].[CompanyId] = [c].[CompanyId]
INNER JOIN [Job].[Jobs] AS [j] ON [m].[JobId] = [j].[JobId]
INNER JOIN [Job].[AppliedJobs] AS [a] ON [m].[CompanyId] = [a].[CompanyId]
WHERE ((([a].[JobId] = [m].[JobId]) AND ([m].[CandidateId] = @__candidateId_0)) AND ([m].[IsDelete] = 0)) AND ([a].[CandidateId] = @__candidateId_0)

SELECT DISTINCT [m].[CandidateId], [m].[JobId], [j].[JobTitle], [m].[CompanyId], [c].[CompanyName], COALESCE((
    SELECT TOP(1) [s].[StatusId]
    FROM [Job].[AppliedJobs] AS [s]
    WHERE (([s].[CandidateId] = [m].[CandidateId]) AND ([s].[JobId] = [m].[JobId])) AND ([s].[CompanyId] = [m].[CompanyId])
    ORDER BY [s].[ApplicationId] DESC
), 0) AS [StatusId], [a].[ApplicationId], CAST(COALESCE((
    SELECT TOP(1) [sm].[IsReceivedCandidate]
    FROM [Common].[Message] AS [sm]
    WHERE (([sm].[CandidateId] = [m].[CandidateId]) AND ([sm].[JobId] = [m].[JobId])) AND ([sm].[CompanyId] = [m].[CompanyId])
    ORDER BY [sm].[SendingTime] DESC
), 0) AS bit) AS [IsReceivedCandidate], CAST(COALESCE((
    SELECT TOP(1) [sm0].[IsReceivedEmploye]
    FROM [Common].[Message] AS [sm0]
    WHERE (([sm0].[CandidateId] = [m].[CandidateId]) AND ([sm0].[JobId] = [m].[JobId])) AND ([sm0].[CompanyId] = [m].[CompanyId])
    ORDER BY [sm0].[SendingTime] DESC
), 0) AS bit) AS [IsReceivedEmploye], COALESCE((
    SELECT TOP(1) [sm1].[SendingTime]
    FROM [Common].[Message] AS [sm1]
    WHERE (([sm1].[CandidateId] = [m].[CandidateId]) AND ([sm1].[JobId] = [m].[JobId])) AND ([sm1].[CompanyId] = [m].[CompanyId])
    ORDER BY [sm1].[SendingTime] DESC
), '0001-01-01T00:00:00.000') AS [LastSendingTime], (
    SELECT TOP(1) [sm2].[MessageBody]
    FROM [Common].[Message] AS [sm2]
    WHERE ((([sm2].[CandidateId] = [m].[CandidateId]) AND ([sm2].[JobId] = [m].[JobId])) AND ([sm2].[CompanyId] = [m].[CompanyId])) AND ([sm2].[IsDelete] = 0)
    ORDER BY [sm2].[SendingTime] DESC
) AS [LastSendingMessage]
FROM [Common].[Message] AS [m]
INNER JOIN [Job].[Companies] AS [c] ON [m].[CompanyId] = [c].[CompanyId]
INNER JOIN [Job].[Jobs] AS [j] ON [m].[JobId] = [j].[JobId]
INNER JOIN [Job].[AppliedJobs] AS [a] ON [m].[CompanyId] = [a].[CompanyId]
WHERE ((([a].[JobId] = [m].[JobId]) AND ([m].[CandidateId] = @__candidateId_0)) AND ([m].[IsDelete] = 0)) AND ([a].[CandidateId] = @__candidateId_0)

SELECT DISTINCT [m].[CandidateId], [m].[JobId], [j].[JobTitle], [m].[CompanyId], [c].[CompanyName], COALESCE((
    SELECT TOP(1) [s].[StatusId]
    FROM [Job].[AppliedJobs] AS [s]
    WHERE (([s].[CandidateId] = [m].[CandidateId]) AND ([s].[JobId] = [m].[JobId])) AND ([s].[CompanyId] = [m].[CompanyId])
    ORDER BY [s].[ApplicationId] DESC
), 0) AS [StatusId], [a].[ApplicationId], CAST(COALESCE((
    SELECT TOP(1) [sm].[IsReceivedCandidate]
    FROM [Common].[Message] AS [sm]
    WHERE (([sm].[CandidateId] = [m].[CandidateId]) AND ([sm].[JobId] = [m].[JobId])) AND ([sm].[CompanyId] = [m].[CompanyId])
    ORDER BY [sm].[SendingTime] DESC
), 0) AS bit) AS [IsReceivedCandidate], CAST(COALESCE((
    SELECT TOP(1) [sm0].[IsReceivedEmploye]
    FROM [Common].[Message] AS [sm0]
    WHERE (([sm0].[CandidateId] = [m].[CandidateId]) AND ([sm0].[JobId] = [m].[JobId])) AND ([sm0].[CompanyId] = [m].[CompanyId])
    ORDER BY [sm0].[SendingTime] DESC
), 0) AS bit) AS [IsReceivedEmploye], COALESCE((
    SELECT TOP(1) [sm1].[SendingTime]
    FROM [Common].[Message] AS [sm1]
    WHERE (([sm1].[CandidateId] = [m].[CandidateId]) AND ([sm1].[JobId] = [m].[JobId])) AND ([sm1].[CompanyId] = [m].[CompanyId])
    ORDER BY [sm1].[SendingTime] DESC
), '0001-01-01T00:00:00.000') AS [LastSendingTime], (
    SELECT TOP(1) [sm2].[MessageBody]
    FROM [Common].[Message] AS [sm2]
    WHERE ((([sm2].[CandidateId] = [m].[CandidateId]) AND ([sm2].[JobId] = [m].[JobId])) AND ([sm2].[CompanyId] = [m].[CompanyId])) AND ([sm2].[IsDelete] = 0)
    ORDER BY [sm2].[SendingTime] DESC
) AS [LastSendingMessage]
FROM [Common].[Message] AS [m]
INNER JOIN [Job].[Companies] AS [c] ON [m].[CompanyId] = [c].[CompanyId]
INNER JOIN [Job].[Jobs] AS [j] ON [m].[JobId] = [j].[JobId]
INNER JOIN [Job].[AppliedJobs] AS [a] ON [m].[CompanyId] = [a].[CompanyId]
WHERE ((([a].[JobId] = [m].[JobId]) AND ([m].[CandidateId] = @__candidateId_0)) AND ([m].[IsDelete] = 0)) AND ([a].[CandidateId] = @__candidateId_0)

SELECT DISTINCT [m].[CandidateId], [m].[JobId], [j].[JobTitle], [m].[CompanyId], [c].[CompanyName], COALESCE((
    SELECT TOP(1) [s].[StatusId]
    FROM [Job].[AppliedJobs] AS [s]
    WHERE (([s].[CandidateId] = [m].[CandidateId]) AND ([s].[JobId] = [m].[JobId])) AND ([s].[CompanyId] = [m].[CompanyId])
    ORDER BY [s].[ApplicationId] DESC
), 0) AS [StatusId], [a].[ApplicationId], CAST(COALESCE((
    SELECT TOP(1) [sm].[IsReceivedCandidate]
    FROM [Common].[Message] AS [sm]
    WHERE (([sm].[CandidateId] = [m].[CandidateId]) AND ([sm].[JobId] = [m].[JobId])) AND ([sm].[CompanyId] = [m].[CompanyId])
    ORDER BY [sm].[SendingTime] DESC
), 0) AS bit) AS [IsReceivedCandidate], CAST(COALESCE((
    SELECT TOP(1) [sm0].[IsReceivedEmploye]
    FROM [Common].[Message] AS [sm0]
    WHERE (([sm0].[CandidateId] = [m].[CandidateId]) AND ([sm0].[JobId] = [m].[JobId])) AND ([sm0].[CompanyId] = [m].[CompanyId])
    ORDER BY [sm0].[SendingTime] DESC
), 0) AS bit) AS [IsReceivedEmploye], COALESCE((
    SELECT TOP(1) [sm1].[SendingTime]
    FROM [Common].[Message] AS [sm1]
    WHERE (([sm1].[CandidateId] = [m].[CandidateId]) AND ([sm1].[JobId] = [m].[JobId])) AND ([sm1].[CompanyId] = [m].[CompanyId])
    ORDER BY [sm1].[SendingTime] DESC
), '0001-01-01T00:00:00.000') AS [LastSendingTime], (
    SELECT TOP(1) [sm2].[MessageBody]
    FROM [Common].[Message] AS [sm2]
    WHERE ((([sm2].[CandidateId] = [m].[CandidateId]) AND ([sm2].[JobId] = [m].[JobId])) AND ([sm2].[CompanyId] = [m].[CompanyId])) AND ([sm2].[IsDelete] = 0)
    ORDER BY [sm2].[SendingTime] DESC
) AS [LastSendingMessage]
FROM [Common].[Message] AS [m]
INNER JOIN [Job].[Companies] AS [c] ON [m].[CompanyId] = [c].[CompanyId]
INNER JOIN [Job].[Jobs] AS [j] ON [m].[JobId] = [j].[JobId]
INNER JOIN [Job].[AppliedJobs] AS [a] ON [m].[CompanyId] = [a].[CompanyId]
WHERE ((([a].[JobId] = [m].[JobId]) AND ([m].[CandidateId] = @__candidateId_0)) AND ([m].[IsDelete] = 0)) AND ([a].[CandidateId] = @__candidateId_0)

SELECT DISTINCT [m].[CandidateId], [m].[JobId], [j].[JobTitle], [m].[CompanyId], [c].[CompanyName], COALESCE((
    SELECT TOP(1) [s].[StatusId]
    FROM [Job].[AppliedJobs] AS [s]
    WHERE (([s].[CandidateId] = [m].[CandidateId]) AND ([s].[JobId] = [m].[JobId])) AND ([s].[CompanyId] = [m].[CompanyId])
    ORDER BY [s].[ApplicationId] DESC
), 0) AS [StatusId], [a].[ApplicationId], CAST(COALESCE((
    SELECT TOP(1) [sm].[IsReceivedCandidate]
    FROM [Common].[Message] AS [sm]
    WHERE (([sm].[CandidateId] = [m].[CandidateId]) AND ([sm].[JobId] = [m].[JobId])) AND ([sm].[CompanyId] = [m].[CompanyId])
    ORDER BY [sm].[SendingTime] DESC
), 0) AS bit) AS [IsReceivedCandidate], CAST(COALESCE((
    SELECT TOP(1) [sm0].[IsReceivedEmploye]
    FROM [Common].[Message] AS [sm0]
    WHERE (([sm0].[CandidateId] = [m].[CandidateId]) AND ([sm0].[JobId] = [m].[JobId])) AND ([sm0].[CompanyId] = [m].[CompanyId])
    ORDER BY [sm0].[SendingTime] DESC
), 0) AS bit) AS [IsReceivedEmploye], COALESCE((
    SELECT TOP(1) [sm1].[SendingTime]
    FROM [Common].[Message] AS [sm1]
    WHERE (([sm1].[CandidateId] = [m].[CandidateId]) AND ([sm1].[JobId] = [m].[JobId])) AND ([sm1].[CompanyId] = [m].[CompanyId])
    ORDER BY [sm1].[SendingTime] DESC
), '0001-01-01T00:00:00.000') AS [LastSendingTime], (
    SELECT TOP(1) [sm2].[MessageBody]
    FROM [Common].[Message] AS [sm2]
    WHERE ((([sm2].[CandidateId] = [m].[CandidateId]) AND ([sm2].[JobId] = [m].[JobId])) AND ([sm2].[CompanyId] = [m].[CompanyId])) AND ([sm2].[IsDelete] = 0)
    ORDER BY [sm2].[SendingTime] DESC
) AS [LastSendingMessage]
FROM [Common].[Message] AS [m]
INNER JOIN [Job].[Companies] AS [c] ON [m].[CompanyId] = [c].[CompanyId]
INNER JOIN [Job].[Jobs] AS [j] ON [m].[JobId] = [j].[JobId]
INNER JOIN [Job].[AppliedJobs] AS [a] ON [m].[CompanyId] = [a].[CompanyId]
WHERE ((([a].[JobId] = [m].[JobId]) AND ([m].[CandidateId] = @__candidateId_0)) AND ([m].[IsDelete] = 0)) AND ([a].[CandidateId] = @__candidateId_0)

SELECT DISTINCT [m].[CandidateId], [m].[JobId], [j].[JobTitle], [m].[CompanyId], [c].[CompanyName], COALESCE((
    SELECT TOP(1) [s].[StatusId]
    FROM [Job].[AppliedJobs] AS [s]
    WHERE (([s].[CandidateId] = [m].[CandidateId]) AND ([s].[JobId] = [m].[JobId])) AND ([s].[CompanyId] = [m].[CompanyId])
    ORDER BY [s].[ApplicationId] DESC
), 0) AS [StatusId], [a].[ApplicationId], CAST(COALESCE((
    SELECT TOP(1) [sm].[IsReceivedCandidate]
    FROM [Common].[Message] AS [sm]
    WHERE (([sm].[CandidateId] = [m].[CandidateId]) AND ([sm].[JobId] = [m].[JobId])) AND ([sm].[CompanyId] = [m].[CompanyId])
    ORDER BY [sm].[SendingTime] DESC
), 0) AS bit) AS [IsReceivedCandidate], CAST(COALESCE((
    SELECT TOP(1) [sm0].[IsReceivedEmploye]
    FROM [Common].[Message] AS [sm0]
    WHERE (([sm0].[CandidateId] = [m].[CandidateId]) AND ([sm0].[JobId] = [m].[JobId])) AND ([sm0].[CompanyId] = [m].[CompanyId])
    ORDER BY [sm0].[SendingTime] DESC
), 0) AS bit) AS [IsReceivedEmploye], COALESCE((
    SELECT TOP(1) [sm1].[SendingTime]
    FROM [Common].[Message] AS [sm1]
    WHERE (([sm1].[CandidateId] = [m].[CandidateId]) AND ([sm1].[JobId] = [m].[JobId])) AND ([sm1].[CompanyId] = [m].[CompanyId])
    ORDER BY [sm1].[SendingTime] DESC
), '0001-01-01T00:00:00.000') AS [LastSendingTime], (
    SELECT TOP(1) [sm2].[MessageBody]
    FROM [Common].[Message] AS [sm2]
    WHERE ((([sm2].[CandidateId] = [m].[CandidateId]) AND ([sm2].[JobId] = [m].[JobId])) AND ([sm2].[CompanyId] = [m].[CompanyId])) AND ([sm2].[IsDelete] = 0)
    ORDER BY [sm2].[SendingTime] DESC
) AS [LastSendingMessage]
FROM [Common].[Message] AS [m]
INNER JOIN [Job].[Companies] AS [c] ON [m].[CompanyId] = [c].[CompanyId]
INNER JOIN [Job].[Jobs] AS [j] ON [m].[JobId] = [j].[JobId]
INNER JOIN [Job].[AppliedJobs] AS [a] ON [m].[CompanyId] = [a].[CompanyId]
WHERE ((([a].[JobId] = [m].[JobId]) AND ([m].[CandidateId] = @__candidateId_0)) AND ([m].[IsDelete] = 0)) AND ([a].[CandidateId] = @__candidateId_0)

SELECT DISTINCT [m].[CandidateId], [m].[JobId], [j].[JobTitle], [m].[CompanyId], [c].[CompanyName], COALESCE((
    SELECT TOP(1) [s].[StatusId]
    FROM [Job].[AppliedJobs] AS [s]
    WHERE (([s].[CandidateId] = [m].[CandidateId]) AND ([s].[JobId] = [m].[JobId])) AND ([s].[CompanyId] = [m].[CompanyId])
    ORDER BY [s].[ApplicationId] DESC
), 0) AS [StatusId], [a].[ApplicationId], CAST(COALESCE((
    SELECT TOP(1) [sm].[IsReceivedCandidate]
    FROM [Common].[Message] AS [sm]
    WHERE (([sm].[CandidateId] = [m].[CandidateId]) AND ([sm].[JobId] = [m].[JobId])) AND ([sm].[CompanyId] = [m].[CompanyId])
    ORDER BY [sm].[SendingTime] DESC
), 0) AS bit) AS [IsReceivedCandidate], CAST(COALESCE((
    SELECT TOP(1) [sm0].[IsReceivedEmploye]
    FROM [Common].[Message] AS [sm0]
    WHERE (([sm0].[CandidateId] = [m].[CandidateId]) AND ([sm0].[JobId] = [m].[JobId])) AND ([sm0].[CompanyId] = [m].[CompanyId])
    ORDER BY [sm0].[SendingTime] DESC
), 0) AS bit) AS [IsReceivedEmploye], COALESCE((
    SELECT TOP(1) [sm1].[SendingTime]
    FROM [Common].[Message] AS [sm1]
    WHERE (([sm1].[CandidateId] = [m].[CandidateId]) AND ([sm1].[JobId] = [m].[JobId])) AND ([sm1].[CompanyId] = [m].[CompanyId])
    ORDER BY [sm1].[SendingTime] DESC
), '0001-01-01T00:00:00.000') AS [LastSendingTime], (
    SELECT TOP(1) [sm2].[MessageBody]
    FROM [Common].[Message] AS [sm2]
    WHERE ((([sm2].[CandidateId] = [m].[CandidateId]) AND ([sm2].[JobId] = [m].[JobId])) AND ([sm2].[CompanyId] = [m].[CompanyId])) AND ([sm2].[IsDelete] = 0)
    ORDER BY [sm2].[SendingTime] DESC
) AS [LastSendingMessage]
FROM [Common].[Message] AS [m]
INNER JOIN [Job].[Companies] AS [c] ON [m].[CompanyId] = [c].[CompanyId]
INNER JOIN [Job].[Jobs] AS [j] ON [m].[JobId] = [j].[JobId]
INNER JOIN [Job].[AppliedJobs] AS [a] ON [m].[CompanyId] = [a].[CompanyId]
WHERE ((([a].[JobId] = [m].[JobId]) AND ([m].[CandidateId] = @__candidateId_0)) AND ([m].[IsDelete] = 0)) AND ([a].[CandidateId] = @__candidateId_0)

SELECT DISTINCT [m].[CandidateId], [m].[JobId], [j].[JobTitle], [m].[CompanyId], [c].[CompanyName], COALESCE((
    SELECT TOP(1) [s].[StatusId]
    FROM [Job].[AppliedJobs] AS [s]
    WHERE (([s].[CandidateId] = [m].[CandidateId]) AND ([s].[JobId] = [m].[JobId])) AND ([s].[CompanyId] = [m].[CompanyId])
    ORDER BY [s].[ApplicationId] DESC
), 0) AS [StatusId], [a].[ApplicationId], CAST(COALESCE((
    SELECT TOP(1) [sm].[IsReceivedCandidate]
    FROM [Common].[Message] AS [sm]
    WHERE (([sm].[CandidateId] = [m].[CandidateId]) AND ([sm].[JobId] = [m].[JobId])) AND ([sm].[CompanyId] = [m].[CompanyId])
    ORDER BY [sm].[SendingTime] DESC
), 0) AS bit) AS [IsReceivedCandidate], CAST(COALESCE((
    SELECT TOP(1) [sm0].[IsReceivedEmploye]
    FROM [Common].[Message] AS [sm0]
    WHERE (([sm0].[CandidateId] = [m].[CandidateId]) AND ([sm0].[JobId] = [m].[JobId])) AND ([sm0].[CompanyId] = [m].[CompanyId])
    ORDER BY [sm0].[SendingTime] DESC
), 0) AS bit) AS [IsReceivedEmploye], COALESCE((
    SELECT TOP(1) [sm1].[SendingTime]
    FROM [Common].[Message] AS [sm1]
    WHERE (([sm1].[CandidateId] = [m].[CandidateId]) AND ([sm1].[JobId] = [m].[JobId])) AND ([sm1].[CompanyId] = [m].[CompanyId])
    ORDER BY [sm1].[SendingTime] DESC
), '0001-01-01T00:00:00.000') AS [LastSendingTime], (
    SELECT TOP(1) [sm2].[MessageBody]
    FROM [Common].[Message] AS [sm2]
    WHERE ((([sm2].[CandidateId] = [m].[CandidateId]) AND ([sm2].[JobId] = [m].[JobId])) AND ([sm2].[CompanyId] = [m].[CompanyId])) AND ([sm2].[IsDelete] = 0)
    ORDER BY [sm2].[SendingTime] DESC
) AS [LastSendingMessage]
FROM [Common].[Message] AS [m]
INNER JOIN [Job].[Companies] AS [c] ON [m].[CompanyId] = [c].[CompanyId]
INNER JOIN [Job].[Jobs] AS [j] ON [m].[JobId] = [j].[JobId]
INNER JOIN [Job].[AppliedJobs] AS [a] ON [m].[CompanyId] = [a].[CompanyId]
WHERE ((([a].[JobId] = [m].[JobId]) AND ([m].[CandidateId] = @__candidateId_0)) AND ([m].[IsDelete] = 0)) AND ([a].[CandidateId] = @__candidateId_0)

), 0) AS [StatusId], [a].[ApplicationId], CAST(COALESCE((

SELECT DISTINCT [m].[CandidateId], [m].[JobId], [j].[JobTitle], [m].[CompanyId], [c].[CompanyName], COALESCE((
    SELECT TOP(1) [s].[StatusId]
    FROM [Job].[AppliedJobs] AS [s]
    WHERE (([s].[CandidateId] = [m].[CandidateId]) AND ([s].[JobId] = [m].[JobId])) AND ([s].[CompanyId] = [m].[CompanyId])
    ORDER BY [s].[ApplicationId] DESC
), 0) AS [StatusId], [a].[ApplicationId], CAST(COALESCE((
    SELECT TOP(1) [sm].[IsReceivedCandidate]
    FROM [Common].[Message] AS [sm]
    WHERE (([sm].[CandidateId] = [m].[CandidateId]) AND ([sm].[JobId] = [m].[JobId])) AND ([sm].[CompanyId] = [m].[CompanyId])
    ORDER BY [sm].[SendingTime] DESC
), 0) AS bit) AS [IsReceivedCandidate], CAST(COALESCE((
    SELECT TOP(1) [sm0].[IsReceivedEmploye]
    FROM [Common].[Message] AS [sm0]
    WHERE (([sm0].[CandidateId] = [m].[CandidateId]) AND ([sm0].[JobId] = [m].[JobId])) AND ([sm0].[CompanyId] = [m].[CompanyId])
    ORDER BY [sm0].[SendingTime] DESC
), 0) AS bit) AS [IsReceivedEmploye], COALESCE((
    SELECT TOP(1) [sm1].[SendingTime]
    FROM [Common].[Message] AS [sm1]
    WHERE (([sm1].[CandidateId] = [m].[CandidateId]) AND ([sm1].[JobId] = [m].[JobId])) AND ([sm1].[CompanyId] = [m].[CompanyId])
    ORDER BY [sm1].[SendingTime] DESC
), '0001-01-01T00:00:00.000') AS [LastSendingTime], (
    SELECT TOP(1) [sm2].[MessageBody]
    FROM [Common].[Message] AS [sm2]
    WHERE ((([sm2].[CandidateId] = [m].[CandidateId]) AND ([sm2].[JobId] = [m].[JobId])) AND ([sm2].[CompanyId] = [m].[CompanyId])) AND ([sm2].[IsDelete] = 0)
    ORDER BY [sm2].[SendingTime] DESC
) AS [LastSendingMessage]
FROM [Common].[Message] AS [m]
INNER JOIN [Job].[Companies] AS [c] ON [m].[CompanyId] = [c].[CompanyId]
INNER JOIN [Job].[Jobs] AS [j] ON [m].[JobId] = [j].[JobId]
INNER JOIN [Job].[AppliedJobs] AS [a] ON [m].[CompanyId] = [a].[CompanyId]
WHERE ((([a].[JobId] = [m].[JobId]) AND ([m].[CandidateId] = @__candidateId_0)) AND ([m].[IsDelete] = 0)) AND ([a].[CandidateId] = @__candidateId_0)

SELECT DISTINCT [m].[CandidateId], [m].[JobId], [j].[JobTitle], [m].[CompanyId], [c].[CompanyName], COALESCE((
    SELECT TOP(1) [s].[StatusId]
    FROM [Job].[AppliedJobs] AS [s]
    WHERE (([s].[CandidateId] = [m].[CandidateId]) AND ([s].[JobId] = [m].[JobId])) AND ([s].[CompanyId] = [m].[CompanyId])
    ORDER BY [s].[ApplicationId] DESC
), 0) AS [StatusId], [a].[ApplicationId], CAST(COALESCE((
    SELECT TOP(1) [sm].[IsReceivedCandidate]
    FROM [Common].[Message] AS [sm]
    WHERE (([sm].[CandidateId] = [m].[CandidateId]) AND ([sm].[JobId] = [m].[JobId])) AND ([sm].[CompanyId] = [m].[CompanyId])
    ORDER BY [sm].[SendingTime] DESC
), 0) AS bit) AS [IsReceivedCandidate], CAST(COALESCE((
    SELECT TOP(1) [sm0].[IsReceivedEmploye]
    FROM [Common].[Message] AS [sm0]
    WHERE (([sm0].[CandidateId] = [m].[CandidateId]) AND ([sm0].[JobId] = [m].[JobId])) AND ([sm0].[CompanyId] = [m].[CompanyId])
    ORDER BY [sm0].[SendingTime] DESC
), 0) AS bit) AS [IsReceivedEmploye], COALESCE((
    SELECT TOP(1) [sm1].[SendingTime]
    FROM [Common].[Message] AS [sm1]
    WHERE (([sm1].[CandidateId] = [m].[CandidateId]) AND ([sm1].[JobId] = [m].[JobId])) AND ([sm1].[CompanyId] = [m].[CompanyId])
    ORDER BY [sm1].[SendingTime] DESC
), '0001-01-01T00:00:00.000') AS [LastSendingTime], (
    SELECT TOP(1) [sm2].[MessageBody]
    FROM [Common].[Message] AS [sm2]
    WHERE ((([sm2].[CandidateId] = [m].[CandidateId]) AND ([sm2].[JobId] = [m].[JobId])) AND ([sm2].[CompanyId] = [m].[CompanyId])) AND ([sm2].[IsDelete] = 0)
    ORDER BY [sm2].[SendingTime] DESC
) AS [LastSendingMessage]
FROM [Common].[Message] AS [m]
INNER JOIN [Job].[Companies] AS [c] ON [m].[CompanyId] = [c].[CompanyId]
INNER JOIN [Job].[Jobs] AS [j] ON [m].[JobId] = [j].[JobId]
INNER JOIN [Job].[AppliedJobs] AS [a] ON [m].[CompanyId] = [a].[CompanyId]
WHERE ((([a].[JobId] = [m].[JobId]) AND ([m].[CandidateId] = @__candidateId_0)) AND ([m].[IsDelete] = 0)) AND ([a].[CandidateId] = @__candidateId_0)

SELECT DISTINCT [m].[CandidateId], [m].[JobId], [j].[JobTitle], [m].[CompanyId], [c].[CompanyName], COALESCE((
    SELECT TOP(1) [s].[StatusId]
    FROM [Job].[AppliedJobs] AS [s]
    WHERE (([s].[CandidateId] = [m].[CandidateId]) AND ([s].[JobId] = [m].[JobId])) AND ([s].[CompanyId] = [m].[CompanyId])
    ORDER BY [s].[ApplicationId] DESC
), 0) AS [StatusId], [a].[ApplicationId], CAST(COALESCE((
    SELECT TOP(1) [sm].[IsReceivedCandidate]
    FROM [Common].[Message] AS [sm]
    WHERE (([sm].[CandidateId] = [m].[CandidateId]) AND ([sm].[JobId] = [m].[JobId])) AND ([sm].[CompanyId] = [m].[CompanyId])
    ORDER BY [sm].[SendingTime] DESC
), 0) AS bit) AS [IsReceivedCandidate], CAST(COALESCE((
    SELECT TOP(1) [sm0].[IsReceivedEmploye]
    FROM [Common].[Message] AS [sm0]
    WHERE (([sm0].[CandidateId] = [m].[CandidateId]) AND ([sm0].[JobId] = [m].[JobId])) AND ([sm0].[CompanyId] = [m].[CompanyId])
    ORDER BY [sm0].[SendingTime] DESC
), 0) AS bit) AS [IsReceivedEmploye], COALESCE((
    SELECT TOP(1) [sm1].[SendingTime]
    FROM [Common].[Message] AS [sm1]
    WHERE (([sm1].[CandidateId] = [m].[CandidateId]) AND ([sm1].[JobId] = [m].[JobId])) AND ([sm1].[CompanyId] = [m].[CompanyId])
    ORDER BY [sm1].[SendingTime] DESC
), '0001-01-01T00:00:00.000') AS [LastSendingTime], (
    SELECT TOP(1) [sm2].[MessageBody]
    FROM [Common].[Message] AS [sm2]
    WHERE ((([sm2].[CandidateId] = [m].[CandidateId]) AND ([sm2].[JobId] = [m].[JobId])) AND ([sm2].[CompanyId] = [m].[CompanyId])) AND ([sm2].[IsDelete] = 0)
    ORDER BY [sm2].[SendingTime] DESC
) AS [LastSendingMessage]
FROM [Common].[Message] AS [m]
INNER JOIN [Job].[Companies] AS [c] ON [m].[CompanyId] = [c].[CompanyId]
INNER JOIN [Job].[Jobs] AS [j] ON [m].[JobId] = [j].[JobId]
INNER JOIN [Job].[AppliedJobs] AS [a] ON [m].[CompanyId] = [a].[CompanyId]
WHERE ((([a].[JobId] = [m].[JobId]) AND ([m].[CandidateId] = @__candidateId_0)) AND ([m].[IsDelete] = 0)) AND ([a].[CandidateId] = @__candidateId_0)

SELECT DISTINCT [m].[CandidateId], [m].[JobId], [j].[JobTitle], [m].[CompanyId], [c].[CompanyName], COALESCE((
    SELECT TOP(1) [s].[StatusId]
    FROM [Job].[AppliedJobs] AS [s]
    WHERE (([s].[CandidateId] = [m].[CandidateId]) AND ([s].[JobId] = [m].[JobId])) AND ([s].[CompanyId] = [m].[CompanyId])
    ORDER BY [s].[ApplicationId] DESC
), 0) AS [StatusId], [a].[ApplicationId], CAST(COALESCE((
    SELECT TOP(1) [sm].[IsReceivedCandidate]
    FROM [Common].[Message] AS [sm]
    WHERE (([sm].[CandidateId] = [m].[CandidateId]) AND ([sm].[JobId] = [m].[JobId])) AND ([sm].[CompanyId] = [m].[CompanyId])
    ORDER BY [sm].[SendingTime] DESC
), 0) AS bit) AS [IsReceivedCandidate], CAST(COALESCE((
    SELECT TOP(1) [sm0].[IsReceivedEmploye]
    FROM [Common].[Message] AS [sm0]
    WHERE (([sm0].[CandidateId] = [m].[CandidateId]) AND ([sm0].[JobId] = [m].[JobId])) AND ([sm0].[CompanyId] = [m].[CompanyId])
    ORDER BY [sm0].[SendingTime] DESC
), 0) AS bit) AS [IsReceivedEmploye], COALESCE((
    SELECT TOP(1) [sm1].[SendingTime]
    FROM [Common].[Message] AS [sm1]
    WHERE (([sm1].[CandidateId] = [m].[CandidateId]) AND ([sm1].[JobId] = [m].[JobId])) AND ([sm1].[CompanyId] = [m].[CompanyId])
    ORDER BY [sm1].[SendingTime] DESC
), '0001-01-01T00:00:00.000') AS [LastSendingTime], (
    SELECT TOP(1) [sm2].[MessageBody]
    FROM [Common].[Message] AS [sm2]
    WHERE ((([sm2].[CandidateId] = [m].[CandidateId]) AND ([sm2].[JobId] = [m].[JobId])) AND ([sm2].[CompanyId] = [m].[CompanyId])) AND ([sm2].[IsDelete] = 0)
    ORDER BY [sm2].[SendingTime] DESC
) AS [LastSendingMessage]
FROM [Common].[Message] AS [m]
INNER JOIN [Job].[Companies] AS [c] ON [m].[CompanyId] = [c].[CompanyId]
INNER JOIN [Job].[Jobs] AS [j] ON [m].[JobId] = [j].[JobId]
INNER JOIN [Job].[AppliedJobs] AS [a] ON [m].[CompanyId] = [a].[CompanyId]
WHERE ((([a].[JobId] = [m].[JobId]) AND ([m].[CandidateId] = @__candidateId_0)) AND ([m].[IsDelete] = 0)) AND ([a].[CandidateId] = @__candidateId_0)

    THEN GETDATE() ELSE [eh].[EndDate]
END AS [EndDate], [eh].[Organization], [eh].[Designation], [eh].[IsCurrentJob]
FROM [Candidate].[EmploymentHistory] AS [eh]
WHERE [eh].[CandidateId] = @__candidateId_2
ORDER BY [eh].[EndDate] DESC, [eh].[StartDate] DESC

SELECT [eh].[EmploymentId], [eh].[CandidateId], [eh].[StartDate], CASE
    WHEN [eh].[IsCurrentJob] = 1
    THEN GETDATE() ELSE [eh].[EndDate]
END AS [EndDate], [eh].[Organization], [eh].[Designation], [eh].[IsCurrentJob]
FROM [Candidate].[EmploymentHistory] AS [eh]
WHERE [eh].[CandidateId] = @__candidateId_2
ORDER BY [eh].[EndDate] DESC, [eh].[StartDate] DESC

    THEN GETDATE() ELSE [eh].[EndDate]

    SELECT TOP(1) [s].[StatusId]
    FROM [Job].[AppliedJobs] AS [s]
    WHERE (([s].[CandidateId] = [m].[CandidateId]) AND ([s].[JobId] = [m].[JobId])) AND ([s].[CompanyId] = [m].[CompanyId])
    ORDER BY [s].[ApplicationId] DESC
), 0) AS [StatusId], [a].[ApplicationId], CAST(COALESCE((
    SELECT TOP(1) [sm].[IsReceivedCandidate]
    FROM [Common].[Message] AS [sm]
    WHERE (([sm].[CandidateId] = [m].[CandidateId]) AND ([sm].[JobId] = [m].[JobId])) AND ([sm].[CompanyId] = [m].[CompanyId])
    ORDER BY [sm].[SendingTime] DESC
), 0) AS bit) AS [IsReceivedCandidate], CAST(COALESCE((
    SELECT TOP(1) [sm0].[IsReceivedEmploye]
    FROM [Common].[Message] AS [sm0]
    WHERE (([sm0].[CandidateId] = [m].[CandidateId]) AND ([sm0].[JobId] = [m].[JobId])) AND ([sm0].[CompanyId] = [m].[CompanyId])
    ORDER BY [sm0].[SendingTime] DESC
), 0) AS bit) AS [IsReceivedEmploye], COALESCE((
    SELECT TOP(1) [sm1].[SendingTime]
    FROM [Common].[Message] AS [sm1]
    WHERE (([sm1].[CandidateId] = [m].[CandidateId]) AND ([sm1].[JobId] = [m].[JobId])) AND ([sm1].[CompanyId] = [m].[CompanyId])
    ORDER BY [sm1].[SendingTime] DESC
), '0001-01-01T00:00:00.000') AS [LastSendingTime], (
    SELECT TOP(1) [sm2].[MessageBody]
    FROM [Common].[Message] AS [sm2]
    WHERE ((([sm2].[CandidateId] = [m].[CandidateId]) AND ([sm2].[JobId] = [m].[JobId])) AND ([sm2].[CompanyId] = [m].[CompanyId])) AND ([sm2].[IsDelete] = 0)
    ORDER BY [sm2].[SendingTime] DESC
) AS [LastSendingMessage]
FROM [Common].[Message] AS [m]
INNER JOIN [Candidate].[Candidates] AS [c] ON [m].[CandidateId] = [c].[CandidateId]
INNER JOIN [Job].[Jobs] AS [j] ON [m].[JobId] = [j].[JobId]
INNER JOIN [Job].[AppliedJobs] AS [a] ON [m].[CandidateId] = [a].[CandidateId]

SELECT DISTINCT [m].[CandidateId], [c].[CandidateName], [m].[JobId], [j].[JobTitle], [m].[CompanyId], COALESCE((
    SELECT TOP(1) [s].[StatusId]
    FROM [Job].[AppliedJobs] AS [s]
    WHERE (([s].[CandidateId] = [m].[CandidateId]) AND ([s].[JobId] = [m].[JobId])) AND ([s].[CompanyId] = [m].[CompanyId])
    ORDER BY [s].[ApplicationId] DESC
), 0) AS [StatusId], [a].[ApplicationId], CAST(COALESCE((
    SELECT TOP(1) [sm].[IsReceivedCandidate]
    FROM [Common].[Message] AS [sm]
    WHERE (([sm].[CandidateId] = [m].[CandidateId]) AND ([sm].[JobId] = [m].[JobId])) AND ([sm].[CompanyId] = [m].[CompanyId])
    ORDER BY [sm].[SendingTime] DESC
), 0) AS bit) AS [IsReceivedCandidate], CAST(COALESCE((
    SELECT TOP(1) [sm0].[IsReceivedEmploye]
    FROM [Common].[Message] AS [sm0]
    WHERE (([sm0].[CandidateId] = [m].[CandidateId]) AND ([sm0].[JobId] = [m].[JobId])) AND ([sm0].[CompanyId] = [m].[CompanyId])
    ORDER BY [sm0].[SendingTime] DESC
), 0) AS bit) AS [IsReceivedEmploye], COALESCE((
    SELECT TOP(1) [sm1].[SendingTime]
    FROM [Common].[Message] AS [sm1]
    WHERE (([sm1].[CandidateId] = [m].[CandidateId]) AND ([sm1].[JobId] = [m].[JobId])) AND ([sm1].[CompanyId] = [m].[CompanyId])
    ORDER BY [sm1].[SendingTime] DESC
), '0001-01-01T00:00:00.000') AS [LastSendingTime], (
    SELECT TOP(1) [sm2].[MessageBody]
    FROM [Common].[Message] AS [sm2]
    WHERE ((([sm2].[CandidateId] = [m].[CandidateId]) AND ([sm2].[JobId] = [m].[JobId])) AND ([sm2].[CompanyId] = [m].[CompanyId])) AND ([sm2].[IsDelete] = 0)
    ORDER BY [sm2].[SendingTime] DESC
) AS [LastSendingMessage]
FROM [Common].[Message] AS [m]
INNER JOIN [Candidate].[Candidates] AS [c] ON [m].[CandidateId] = [c].[CandidateId]
INNER JOIN [Job].[Jobs] AS [j] ON [m].[JobId] = [j].[JobId]
INNER JOIN [Job].[AppliedJobs] AS [a] ON [m].[CandidateId] = [a].[CandidateId]
WHERE (([a].[JobId] = [m].[JobId]) AND ([m].[CompanyId] = @__companyId_0)) AND ([m].[IsDelete] = 0)

    SELECT TOP(1) [sm1].[SendingTime]
    FROM [Common].[Message] AS [sm1]
    WHERE (([sm1].[CandidateId] = [m].[CandidateId]) AND ([sm1].[JobId] = [m].[JobId])) AND ([sm1].[CompanyId] = [m].[CompanyId])
    ORDER BY [sm1].[SendingTime] DESC
), '0001-01-01T00:00:00.000') AS [LastSendingTime], (
    SELECT TOP(1) [sm2].[MessageBody]
    FROM [Common].[Message] AS [sm2]
    WHERE ((([sm2].[CandidateId] = [m].[CandidateId]) AND ([sm2].[JobId] = [m].[JobId])) AND ([sm2].[CompanyId] = [m].[CompanyId])) AND ([sm2].[IsDelete] = 0)
    ORDER BY [sm2].[SendingTime] DESC
) AS [LastSendingMessage]
FROM [Common].[Message] AS [m]
INNER JOIN [Candidate].[Candidates] AS [c] ON [m].[CandidateId] = [c].[CandidateId]
INNER JOIN [Job].[Jobs] AS [j] ON [m].[JobId] = [j].[JobId]
INNER JOIN [Job].[AppliedJobs] AS [a] ON [m].[CandidateId] = [a].[CandidateId]
WHERE (([a].[JobId] = [m].[JobId]) AND ([m].[CompanyId] = @__companyId_0)) AND ([m].[IsDelete] = 0)

SELECT DISTINCT [m].[CandidateId], [c].[CandidateName], [m].[JobId], [j].[JobTitle], [m].[CompanyId], COALESCE((
    SELECT TOP(1) [s].[StatusId]
    FROM [Job].[AppliedJobs] AS [s]
    WHERE (([s].[CandidateId] = [m].[CandidateId]) AND ([s].[JobId] = [m].[JobId])) AND ([s].[CompanyId] = [m].[CompanyId])
    ORDER BY [s].[ApplicationId] DESC
), 0) AS [StatusId], [a].[ApplicationId], CAST(COALESCE((
    SELECT TOP(1) [sm].[IsReceivedCandidate]
    FROM [Common].[Message] AS [sm]
    WHERE (([sm].[CandidateId] = [m].[CandidateId]) AND ([sm].[JobId] = [m].[JobId])) AND ([sm].[CompanyId] = [m].[CompanyId])
    ORDER BY [sm].[SendingTime] DESC
), 0) AS bit) AS [IsReceivedCandidate], CAST(COALESCE((
    SELECT TOP(1) [sm0].[IsReceivedEmploye]
    FROM [Common].[Message] AS [sm0]
    WHERE (([sm0].[CandidateId] = [m].[CandidateId]) AND ([sm0].[JobId] = [m].[JobId])) AND ([sm0].[CompanyId] = [m].[CompanyId])
    ORDER BY [sm0].[SendingTime] DESC
), 0) AS bit) AS [IsReceivedEmploye], COALESCE((
    SELECT TOP(1) [sm1].[SendingTime]
    FROM [Common].[Message] AS [sm1]

    ORDER BY [sm1].[SendingTime] DESC
), '0001-01-01T00:00:00.000') AS [LastSendingTime], (

) AS [LastSendingMessage]

    SELECT TOP(1) [s].[StatusId]
    FROM [Job].[AppliedJobs] AS [s]
    WHERE (([s].[CandidateId] = [m].[CandidateId]) AND ([s].[JobId] = [m].[JobId])) AND ([s].[CompanyId] = [m].[CompanyId])
    ORDER BY [s].[ApplicationId] DESC
), 0) AS [StatusId], [a].[ApplicationId], CAST(COALESCE((
    SELECT TOP(1) [sm].[IsReceivedCandidate]
    FROM [Common].[Message] AS [sm]
    WHERE (([sm].[CandidateId] = [m].[CandidateId]) AND ([sm].[JobId] = [m].[JobId])) AND ([sm].[CompanyId] = [m].[CompanyId])
    ORDER BY [sm].[SendingTime] DESC
), 0) AS bit) AS [IsReceivedCandidate], CAST(COALESCE((
    SELECT TOP(1) [sm0].[IsReceivedEmploye]
    FROM [Common].[Message] AS [sm0]
    WHERE (([sm0].[CandidateId] = [m].[CandidateId]) AND ([sm0].[JobId] = [m].[JobId])) AND ([sm0].[CompanyId] = [m].[CompanyId])
    ORDER BY [sm0].[SendingTime] DESC
), 0) AS bit) AS [IsReceivedEmploye], COALESCE((
    SELECT TOP(1) [sm1].[SendingTime]
    FROM [Common].[Message] AS [sm1]
    WHERE (([sm1].[CandidateId] = [m].[CandidateId]) AND ([sm1].[JobId] = [m].[JobId])) AND ([sm1].[CompanyId] = [m].[CompanyId])
    ORDER BY [sm1].[SendingTime] DESC
), '0001-01-01T00:00:00.000') AS [LastSendingTime], (
    SELECT TOP(1) [sm2].[MessageBody]
    FROM [Common].[Message] AS [sm2]
    WHERE ((([sm2].[CandidateId] = [m].[CandidateId]) AND ([sm2].[JobId] = [m].[JobId])) AND ([sm2].[CompanyId] = [m].[CompanyId])) AND ([sm2].[IsDelete] = 0)
    ORDER BY [sm2].[SendingTime] DESC
) AS [LastSendingMessage]
FROM [Common].[Message] AS [m]
INNER JOIN [Candidate].[Candidates] AS [c] ON [m].[CandidateId] = [c].[CandidateId]
INNER JOIN [Job].[Jobs] AS [j] ON [m].[JobId] = [j].[JobId]
INNER JOIN [Job].[AppliedJobs] AS [a] ON [m].[CandidateId] = [a].[CandidateId]
WHERE (([a].[JobId] = [m].[JobId]) AND ([m].[CompanyId] = @__companyId_0)) AND ([m].[IsDelete] = 0)

SELECT DISTINCT [m].[CandidateId], [c].[CandidateName], [m].[JobId], [j].[JobTitle], [m].[CompanyId], COALESCE((
    SELECT TOP(1) [s].[StatusId]
    FROM [Job].[AppliedJobs] AS [s]
    WHERE (([s].[CandidateId] = [m].[CandidateId]) AND ([s].[JobId] = [m].[JobId])) AND ([s].[CompanyId] = [m].[CompanyId])
    ORDER BY [s].[ApplicationId] DESC
), 0) AS [StatusId], [a].[ApplicationId], CAST(COALESCE((
    SELECT TOP(1) [sm].[IsReceivedCandidate]
    FROM [Common].[Message] AS [sm]
    WHERE (([sm].[CandidateId] = [m].[CandidateId]) AND ([sm].[JobId] = [m].[JobId])) AND ([sm].[CompanyId] = [m].[CompanyId])
    ORDER BY [sm].[SendingTime] DESC
), 0) AS bit) AS [IsReceivedCandidate], CAST(COALESCE((
    SELECT TOP(1) [sm0].[IsReceivedEmploye]
    FROM [Common].[Message] AS [sm0]
    WHERE (([sm0].[CandidateId] = [m].[CandidateId]) AND ([sm0].[JobId] = [m].[JobId])) AND ([sm0].[CompanyId] = [m].[CompanyId])
    ORDER BY [sm0].[SendingTime] DESC
), 0) AS bit) AS [IsReceivedEmploye], COALESCE((
    SELECT TOP(1) [sm1].[SendingTime]
    FROM [Common].[Message] AS [sm1]
    WHERE (([sm1].[CandidateId] = [m].[CandidateId]) AND ([sm1].[JobId] = [m].[JobId])) AND ([sm1].[CompanyId] = [m].[CompanyId])
    ORDER BY [sm1].[SendingTime] DESC
), '0001-01-01T00:00:00.000') AS [LastSendingTime], (
    SELECT TOP(1) [sm2].[MessageBody]
    FROM [Common].[Message] AS [sm2]
    WHERE ((([sm2].[CandidateId] = [m].[CandidateId]) AND ([sm2].[JobId] = [m].[JobId])) AND ([sm2].[CompanyId] = [m].[CompanyId])) AND ([sm2].[IsDelete] = 0)
    ORDER BY [sm2].[SendingTime] DESC
) AS [LastSendingMessage]
FROM [Common].[Message] AS [m]
INNER JOIN [Candidate].[Candidates] AS [c] ON [m].[CandidateId] = [c].[CandidateId]
INNER JOIN [Job].[Jobs] AS [j] ON [m].[JobId] = [j].[JobId]
INNER JOIN [Job].[AppliedJobs] AS [a] ON [m].[CandidateId] = [a].[CandidateId]
WHERE (([a].[JobId] = [m].[JobId]) AND ([m].[CompanyId] = @__companyId_0)) AND ([m].[IsDelete] = 0)

SELECT DISTINCT [m].[CandidateId], [c].[CandidateName], [m].[JobId], [j].[JobTitle], [m].[CompanyId], COALESCE((
    SELECT TOP(1) [s].[StatusId]
    FROM [Job].[AppliedJobs] AS [s]
    WHERE (([s].[CandidateId] = [m].[CandidateId]) AND ([s].[JobId] = [m].[JobId])) AND ([s].[CompanyId] = [m].[CompanyId])
    ORDER BY [s].[ApplicationId] DESC
), 0) AS [StatusId], [a].[ApplicationId], CAST(COALESCE((
    SELECT TOP(1) [sm].[IsReceivedCandidate]
    FROM [Common].[Message] AS [sm]
    WHERE (([sm].[CandidateId] = [m].[CandidateId]) AND ([sm].[JobId] = [m].[JobId])) AND ([sm].[CompanyId] = [m].[CompanyId])
    ORDER BY [sm].[SendingTime] DESC
), 0) AS bit) AS [IsReceivedCandidate], CAST(COALESCE((
    SELECT TOP(1) [sm0].[IsReceivedEmploye]
    FROM [Common].[Message] AS [sm0]
    WHERE (([sm0].[CandidateId] = [m].[CandidateId]) AND ([sm0].[JobId] = [m].[JobId])) AND ([sm0].[CompanyId] = [m].[CompanyId])
    ORDER BY [sm0].[SendingTime] DESC
), 0) AS bit) AS [IsReceivedEmploye], COALESCE((
    SELECT TOP(1) [sm1].[SendingTime]
    FROM [Common].[Message] AS [sm1]
    WHERE (([sm1].[CandidateId] = [m].[CandidateId]) AND ([sm1].[JobId] = [m].[JobId])) AND ([sm1].[CompanyId] = [m].[CompanyId])
    ORDER BY [sm1].[SendingTime] DESC
), '0001-01-01T00:00:00.000') AS [LastSendingTime], (
    SELECT TOP(1) [sm2].[MessageBody]
    FROM [Common].[Message] AS [sm2]
    WHERE ((([sm2].[CandidateId] = [m].[CandidateId]) AND ([sm2].[JobId] = [m].[JobId])) AND ([sm2].[CompanyId] = [m].[CompanyId])) AND ([sm2].[IsDelete] = 0)
    ORDER BY [sm2].[SendingTime] DESC
) AS [LastSendingMessage]
FROM [Common].[Message] AS [m]
INNER JOIN [Candidate].[Candidates] AS [c] ON [m].[CandidateId] = [c].[CandidateId]
INNER JOIN [Job].[Jobs] AS [j] ON [m].[JobId] = [j].[JobId]
INNER JOIN [Job].[AppliedJobs] AS [a] ON [m].[CandidateId] = [a].[CandidateId]
WHERE (([a].[JobId] = [m].[JobId]) AND ([m].[CompanyId] = @__companyId_0)) AND ([m].[IsDelete] = 0)

    ORDER BY [s].[ApplicationId] DESC
), 0) AS [StatusId], [a].[ApplicationId], CAST(COALESCE((

    FROM [Common].[Message] AS [sm]
    WHERE (([sm].[CandidateId] = [m].[CandidateId]) AND ([sm].[JobId] = [m].[JobId])) AND ([sm].[CompanyId] = [m].[CompanyId])
    ORDER BY [sm].[SendingTime] DESC

SELECT DISTINCT [m].[CandidateId], [c].[CandidateName], [m].[JobId], [j].[JobTitle], [m].[CompanyId], COALESCE((
    SELECT TOP(1) [s].[StatusId]
    FROM [Job].[AppliedJobs] AS [s]
    WHERE (([s].[CandidateId] = [m].[CandidateId]) AND ([s].[JobId] = [m].[JobId])) AND ([s].[CompanyId] = [m].[CompanyId])
    ORDER BY [s].[ApplicationId] DESC
), 0) AS [StatusId], [a].[ApplicationId], CAST(COALESCE((
    SELECT TOP(1) [sm].[IsReceivedCandidate]
    FROM [Common].[Message] AS [sm]
    WHERE (([sm].[CandidateId] = [m].[CandidateId]) AND ([sm].[JobId] = [m].[JobId])) AND ([sm].[CompanyId] = [m].[CompanyId])
    ORDER BY [sm].[SendingTime] DESC
), 0) AS bit) AS [IsReceivedCandidate], CAST(COALESCE((
    SELECT TOP(1) [sm0].[IsReceivedEmploye]
    FROM [Common].[Message] AS [sm0]
    WHERE (([sm0].[CandidateId] = [m].[CandidateId]) AND ([sm0].[JobId] = [m].[JobId])) AND ([sm0].[CompanyId] = [m].[CompanyId])
    ORDER BY [sm0].[SendingTime] DESC
), 0) AS bit) AS [IsReceivedEmploye], COALESCE((
    SELECT TOP(1) [sm1].[SendingTime]
    FROM [Common].[Message] AS [sm1]
    WHERE (([sm1].[CandidateId] = [m].[CandidateId]) AND ([sm1].[JobId] = [m].[JobId])) AND ([sm1].[CompanyId] = [m].[CompanyId])
    ORDER BY [sm1].[SendingTime] DESC
), '0001-01-01T00:00:00.000') AS [LastSendingTime], (
    SELECT TOP(1) [sm2].[MessageBody]
    FROM [Common].[Message] AS [sm2]
    WHERE ((([sm2].[CandidateId] = [m].[CandidateId]) AND ([sm2].[JobId] = [m].[JobId])) AND ([sm2].[CompanyId] = [m].[CompanyId])) AND ([sm2].[IsDelete] = 0)
    ORDER BY [sm2].[SendingTime] DESC
) AS [LastSendingMessage]
FROM [Common].[Message] AS [m]
INNER JOIN [Candidate].[Candidates] AS [c] ON [m].[CandidateId] = [c].[CandidateId]
INNER JOIN [Job].[Jobs] AS [j] ON [m].[JobId] = [j].[JobId]
INNER JOIN [Job].[AppliedJobs] AS [a] ON [m].[CandidateId] = [a].[CandidateId]
WHERE (([a].[JobId] = [m].[JobId]) AND ([m].[CompanyId] = @__companyId_0)) AND ([m].[IsDelete] = 0)

SELECT DISTINCT [m].[CandidateId], [c].[CandidateName], [m].[JobId], [j].[JobTitle], [m].[CompanyId], COALESCE((
    SELECT TOP(1) [s].[StatusId]
    FROM [Job].[AppliedJobs] AS [s]
    WHERE (([s].[CandidateId] = [m].[CandidateId]) AND ([s].[JobId] = [m].[JobId])) AND ([s].[CompanyId] = [m].[CompanyId])
    ORDER BY [s].[ApplicationId] DESC
), 0) AS [StatusId], [a].[ApplicationId], CAST(COALESCE((
    SELECT TOP(1) [sm].[IsReceivedCandidate]
    FROM [Common].[Message] AS [sm]
    WHERE (([sm].[CandidateId] = [m].[CandidateId]) AND ([sm].[JobId] = [m].[JobId])) AND ([sm].[CompanyId] = [m].[CompanyId])
    ORDER BY [sm].[SendingTime] DESC
), 0) AS bit) AS [IsReceivedCandidate], CAST(COALESCE((
    SELECT TOP(1) [sm0].[IsReceivedEmploye]
    FROM [Common].[Message] AS [sm0]
    WHERE (([sm0].[CandidateId] = [m].[CandidateId]) AND ([sm0].[JobId] = [m].[JobId])) AND ([sm0].[CompanyId] = [m].[CompanyId])
    ORDER BY [sm0].[SendingTime] DESC
), 0) AS bit) AS [IsReceivedEmploye], COALESCE((
    SELECT TOP(1) [sm1].[SendingTime]
    FROM [Common].[Message] AS [sm1]
    WHERE (([sm1].[CandidateId] = [m].[CandidateId]) AND ([sm1].[JobId] = [m].[JobId])) AND ([sm1].[CompanyId] = [m].[CompanyId])
    ORDER BY [sm1].[SendingTime] DESC
), '0001-01-01T00:00:00.000') AS [LastSendingTime], (
    SELECT TOP(1) [sm2].[MessageBody]
    FROM [Common].[Message] AS [sm2]
    WHERE ((([sm2].[CandidateId] = [m].[CandidateId]) AND ([sm2].[JobId] = [m].[JobId])) AND ([sm2].[CompanyId] = [m].[CompanyId])) AND ([sm2].[IsDelete] = 0)
    ORDER BY [sm2].[SendingTime] DESC
) AS [LastSendingMessage]
FROM [Common].[Message] AS [m]
INNER JOIN [Candidate].[Candidates] AS [c] ON [m].[CandidateId] = [c].[CandidateId]
INNER JOIN [Job].[Jobs] AS [j] ON [m].[JobId] = [j].[JobId]
INNER JOIN [Job].[AppliedJobs] AS [a] ON [m].[CandidateId] = [a].[CandidateId]
WHERE (([a].[JobId] = [m].[JobId]) AND ([m].[CompanyId] = @__companyId_0)) AND ([m].[IsDelete] = 0)

SELECT DISTINCT [m].[CandidateId], [c].[CandidateName], [m].[JobId], [j].[JobTitle], [m].[CompanyId], COALESCE((
    SELECT TOP(1) [s].[StatusId]
    FROM [Job].[AppliedJobs] AS [s]
    WHERE (([s].[CandidateId] = [m].[CandidateId]) AND ([s].[JobId] = [m].[JobId])) AND ([s].[CompanyId] = [m].[CompanyId])
    ORDER BY [s].[ApplicationId] DESC
), 0) AS [StatusId], [a].[ApplicationId], CAST(COALESCE((
    SELECT TOP(1) [sm].[IsReceivedCandidate]
    FROM [Common].[Message] AS [sm]
    WHERE (([sm].[CandidateId] = [m].[CandidateId]) AND ([sm].[JobId] = [m].[JobId])) AND ([sm].[CompanyId] = [m].[CompanyId])
    ORDER BY [sm].[SendingTime] DESC
), 0) AS bit) AS [IsReceivedCandidate], CAST(COALESCE((
    SELECT TOP(1) [sm0].[IsReceivedEmploye]
    FROM [Common].[Message] AS [sm0]
    WHERE (([sm0].[CandidateId] = [m].[CandidateId]) AND ([sm0].[JobId] = [m].[JobId])) AND ([sm0].[CompanyId] = [m].[CompanyId])
    ORDER BY [sm0].[SendingTime] DESC
), 0) AS bit) AS [IsReceivedEmploye], COALESCE((
    SELECT TOP(1) [sm1].[SendingTime]
    FROM [Common].[Message] AS [sm1]
    WHERE (([sm1].[CandidateId] = [m].[CandidateId]) AND ([sm1].[JobId] = [m].[JobId])) AND ([sm1].[CompanyId] = [m].[CompanyId])
    ORDER BY [sm1].[SendingTime] DESC
), '0001-01-01T00:00:00.000') AS [LastSendingTime], (
    SELECT TOP(1) [sm2].[MessageBody]
    FROM [Common].[Message] AS [sm2]
    WHERE ((([sm2].[CandidateId] = [m].[CandidateId]) AND ([sm2].[JobId] = [m].[JobId])) AND ([sm2].[CompanyId] = [m].[CompanyId])) AND ([sm2].[IsDelete] = 0)
    ORDER BY [sm2].[SendingTime] DESC
) AS [LastSendingMessage]
FROM [Common].[Message] AS [m]
INNER JOIN [Candidate].[Candidates] AS [c] ON [m].[CandidateId] = [c].[CandidateId]
INNER JOIN [Job].[Jobs] AS [j] ON [m].[JobId] = [j].[JobId]
INNER JOIN [Job].[AppliedJobs] AS [a] ON [m].[CandidateId] = [a].[CandidateId]
WHERE (([a].[JobId] = [m].[JobId]) AND ([m].[CompanyId] = @__companyId_0)) AND ([m].[IsDelete] = 0)

    ORDER BY [s].[ApplicationId] DESC
), 0) AS [StatusId], [a].[ApplicationId], CAST(COALESCE((

    FROM [Common].[Message] AS [sm]
    WHERE (([sm].[CandidateId] = [m].[CandidateId]) AND ([sm].[JobId] = [m].[JobId])) AND ([sm].[CompanyId] = [m].[CompanyId])

SELECT DISTINCT [m].[CandidateId], [c].[CandidateName], [m].[JobId], [j].[JobTitle], [m].[CompanyId], COALESCE((
    SELECT TOP(1) [s].[StatusId]
    FROM [Job].[AppliedJobs] AS [s]
    WHERE (([s].[CandidateId] = [m].[CandidateId]) AND ([s].[JobId] = [m].[JobId])) AND ([s].[CompanyId] = [m].[CompanyId])
    ORDER BY [s].[ApplicationId] DESC
), 0) AS [StatusId], [a].[ApplicationId], CAST(COALESCE((
    SELECT TOP(1) [sm].[IsReceivedCandidate]
    FROM [Common].[Message] AS [sm]
    WHERE (([sm].[CandidateId] = [m].[CandidateId]) AND ([sm].[JobId] = [m].[JobId])) AND ([sm].[CompanyId] = [m].[CompanyId])
    ORDER BY [sm].[SendingTime] DESC
), 0) AS bit) AS [IsReceivedCandidate], CAST(COALESCE((
    SELECT TOP(1) [sm0].[IsReceivedEmploye]
    FROM [Common].[Message] AS [sm0]
    WHERE (([sm0].[CandidateId] = [m].[CandidateId]) AND ([sm0].[JobId] = [m].[JobId])) AND ([sm0].[CompanyId] = [m].[CompanyId])
    ORDER BY [sm0].[SendingTime] DESC
), 0) AS bit) AS [IsReceivedEmploye], COALESCE((
    SELECT TOP(1) [sm1].[SendingTime]
    FROM [Common].[Message] AS [sm1]
    WHERE (([sm1].[CandidateId] = [m].[CandidateId]) AND ([sm1].[JobId] = [m].[JobId])) AND ([sm1].[CompanyId] = [m].[CompanyId])
    ORDER BY [sm1].[SendingTime] DESC
), '0001-01-01T00:00:00.000') AS [LastSendingTime], (
    SELECT TOP(1) [sm2].[MessageBody]
    FROM [Common].[Message] AS [sm2]
    WHERE ((([sm2].[CandidateId] = [m].[CandidateId]) AND ([sm2].[JobId] = [m].[JobId])) AND ([sm2].[CompanyId] = [m].[CompanyId])) AND ([sm2].[IsDelete] = 0)
    ORDER BY [sm2].[SendingTime] DESC
) AS [LastSendingMessage]
FROM [Common].[Message] AS [m]
INNER JOIN [Candidate].[Candidates] AS [c] ON [m].[CandidateId] = [c].[CandidateId]
INNER JOIN [Job].[Jobs] AS [j] ON [m].[JobId] = [j].[JobId]
INNER JOIN [Job].[AppliedJobs] AS [a] ON [m].[CandidateId] = [a].[CandidateId]
WHERE (([a].[JobId] = [m].[JobId]) AND ([m].[CompanyId] = @__companyId_0)) AND ([m].[IsDelete] = 0)

SELECT DISTINCT [m].[CandidateId], [c].[CandidateName], [m].[JobId], [j].[JobTitle], [m].[CompanyId], COALESCE((
    SELECT TOP(1) [s].[StatusId]
    FROM [Job].[AppliedJobs] AS [s]
    WHERE (([s].[CandidateId] = [m].[CandidateId]) AND ([s].[JobId] = [m].[JobId])) AND ([s].[CompanyId] = [m].[CompanyId])
    ORDER BY [s].[ApplicationId] DESC
), 0) AS [StatusId], [a].[ApplicationId], CAST(COALESCE((
    SELECT TOP(1) [sm].[IsReceivedCandidate]
    FROM [Common].[Message] AS [sm]
    WHERE (([sm].[CandidateId] = [m].[CandidateId]) AND ([sm].[JobId] = [m].[JobId])) AND ([sm].[CompanyId] = [m].[CompanyId])
    ORDER BY [sm].[SendingTime] DESC
), 0) AS bit) AS [IsReceivedCandidate], CAST(COALESCE((
    SELECT TOP(1) [sm0].[IsReceivedEmploye]
    FROM [Common].[Message] AS [sm0]
    WHERE (([sm0].[CandidateId] = [m].[CandidateId]) AND ([sm0].[JobId] = [m].[JobId])) AND ([sm0].[CompanyId] = [m].[CompanyId])
    ORDER BY [sm0].[SendingTime] DESC
), 0) AS bit) AS [IsReceivedEmploye], COALESCE((
    SELECT TOP(1) [sm1].[SendingTime]
    FROM [Common].[Message] AS [sm1]
    WHERE (([sm1].[CandidateId] = [m].[CandidateId]) AND ([sm1].[JobId] = [m].[JobId])) AND ([sm1].[CompanyId] = [m].[CompanyId])
    ORDER BY [sm1].[SendingTime] DESC
), '0001-01-01T00:00:00.000') AS [LastSendingTime], (
    SELECT TOP(1) [sm2].[MessageBody]
    FROM [Common].[Message] AS [sm2]
    WHERE ((([sm2].[CandidateId] = [m].[CandidateId]) AND ([sm2].[JobId] = [m].[JobId])) AND ([sm2].[CompanyId] = [m].[CompanyId])) AND ([sm2].[IsDelete] = 0)
    ORDER BY [sm2].[SendingTime] DESC
) AS [LastSendingMessage]
FROM [Common].[Message] AS [m]
INNER JOIN [Candidate].[Candidates] AS [c] ON [m].[CandidateId] = [c].[CandidateId]
INNER JOIN [Job].[Jobs] AS [j] ON [m].[JobId] = [j].[JobId]
INNER JOIN [Job].[AppliedJobs] AS [a] ON [m].[CandidateId] = [a].[CandidateId]
WHERE (([a].[JobId] = [m].[JobId]) AND ([m].[CompanyId] = @__companyId_0)) AND ([m].[IsDelete] = 0)
